Monitor the cluster and nodes
- resource usage
- availability and health

Monitor deployments and pods
- missing and failed pods
- running vs. the desired state
- pod resource usage requests and limits

Monitoring applications: 
- application availability 
- application health and performance

Opensource Tools: 

Prometheus
Grafana

